[ti:Cenizas y luz - The Last of Us]
[ar:Unknown]
[al:The Last of Us]
[length:03:20]
[la:en]

[00:10.50]Woke to silence, skies turned grey,
[00:17.70]Footsteps echo far away.
[00:24.80]Dust and shadows, all I’ve known,
[00:31.80]Carry me where seeds are sown.
[00:43.40]In the quiet, I hear your name,
[00:51.70]Through the ashes, through the flame.
[00:59.90]What we lost and what remains,
[01:08.30]I’ll remember through the pain.
[01:18.40]Time moves slow where ghosts still lie,
[01:25.60]Underneath a broken sky.
[01:32.60]Scars and stories mark the land,
[01:40.00]Still I reach to hold your hand.
[01:52.20]In the quiet, I hear your name,
[02:00.10]Through the ashes, through the flame.
[02:08.20]What we lost and what remains,
[02:16.60]I’ll remember through the pain.
[02:31.30]If I fall or lose my way,
[02:38.90]Guide me through the dark today.
[02:46.50]One last song, one final light—
[02:54.00]Hope still flickers in the night.
